'''西德尼·凱瑟琳·鮑威爾''' （{{lang-en|Sidney Katherine Powell}}；{{bd|1955年|||catIdx=P}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n96002132|title=Powell, Sidney K.|access-date=16 November 2020|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120033535/http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n96002132/|dead-url=no}}</ref>是[[美國律師|美國律師]]和前[[聯邦檢察官|州檢察官]]。

1978年從[[法學院|法學院]]畢業後，鮑威爾開始了職業生涯，當時是[[美國德克薩斯西區聯邦地區法院|德克薩斯西區聯邦地區法院]]的助理檢察官。在她任職期間，她起訴了[[毒梟|毒梟]][[吉米·查格拉|吉米·查格拉]]（Jamiel Chagra）<ref name=dallasnews>{{Cite news|first=Elizabeth|last=Thompson|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/2020/11/20/5-things-to-know-about-sidney-powell-the-dallas-lawyer-on-trumps-legal-team-alleging-election-fraud/|title=5 things to know about Sidney Powell, the Dallas lawyer formerly on Trump's legal team|date=November 23, 2020|newspaper=[[:en:The_Dallas_Morning_News|Dallas News]]|accessdate=2020-12-16|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122182645/https://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/2020/11/20/5-things-to-know-about-sidney-powell-the-dallas-lawyer-on-trumps-legal-team-alleging-election-fraud/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1988年，她離開檢察官職務，於1993年成立了自己的公司，曾在各種法律案件中擔任控方或辯方律師<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/article/who-is-sidney-powell.html|title=What We Know About Sidney Powell, the Lawyer Behind Wild Voting Conspiracy Theories|first1=Jeremy W.|last1=Peters|first2=Alan|last2=Feuer|date=November 23, 2020|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]}}</ref><ref name=dallasnews/>。她曾參與的著名案件包括[[安隆醜聞案|安隆醜聞案]]和[[迈克尔·T·弗林|麥可·弗林]]將軍案件的辯護<ref name=":6" /><ref name="maga" />。

2020年，鮑威爾加入了[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]總統的法律團隊，試圖挑戰[[喬·拜登|喬·拜登]]在[[2020年美國總統大選|2020年總統大選]]中的勝利。在幾次採訪中，鮑威爾指控了更多的選舉欺詐陰謀論，特朗普的法律團隊正式與她保持距離，稱她「自己執業」，而不是團隊成員<ref name="wolfe">{{Cite web|last=Wolfe|first=Jan|date=November 22, 2020|title=Trump campaign says Sidney Powell not a member of legal team|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-election-trump-powell-idUSKBN2820UB|agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|access-date=2020-12-16|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124153750/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-election-trump-powell-idUSKBN2820UB|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":5">{{Cite news|last=Bowden|first=John|date=November 22, 2020|title=Giuliani distances Trump campaign from attorney Sidney Powell|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/527105-giuliani-distances-trump-campaign-from-sidney-powell|access-date=November 22, 2020|newspaper=[[The_Hill_(newspaper)|The Hill]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229144658/https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/527105-giuliani-distances-trump-campaign-from-sidney-powell|dead-url=no}}</ref>。鮑威爾繼續在地方法院獨立提起選舉訴訟，結果她在[[密西根州|密西根州]]、[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]、[[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]]和[[威斯康辛州|威斯康辛州]]輸了四次聯邦訴訟。

鮑威爾提出了許多陰謀論。她聲稱弗林將軍是被一個秘密的「[[深層政府|深層政府]]」行動陷害的<ref name="maga" /><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|date=June 12, 2019|title=Michael Flynn hires Dallas lawyer Sidney Powell, a conspiracy theorist who calls Mueller a 'creep'|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/2019/06/12/michael-flynn-hires-dallas-lawyer-sidney-powell-a-conspiracy-theorist-who-calls-mueller-a-creep/|access-date=November 20, 2020|newspaper=Dallas News|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117193736/https://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/2019/06/12/michael-flynn-hires-dallas-lawyer-sidney-powell-a-conspiracy-theorist-who-calls-mueller-a-creep/|url-status=no}}</ref>，並且還提倡了與[[匿名者Q|QAnon]]陰謀論相關的個性和口號。關於2020年總統大選，鮑威爾聲稱，秘密的國際陰謀涉及[[共產黨|共產黨]]人、「[[新世界秩序|新世界秩序]]」、[[喬治·索羅斯|喬治·索羅斯]]、[[烏戈·查維茲|烏戈·查維茲]]、[[克林頓基金會|克林頓基金會]]、[[中央情報局|中央情報局]]以及數千名[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]和[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]官員，包括川普盟友和喬治亞州州長[[布萊恩·肯普|布萊恩·肯普]]，使用投票機將數百萬張選票從川普轉移到拜登<ref>{{Cite news|last=Walsh|first=Joe|date=November 20, 2020|title=Who Is Sidney Powell? Meet Trump's New Top Conspiracy Theorist|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/joewalsh/2020/11/20/who-is-sidney-powell-meet-trumps-new-top-conspiracy-theorist/?sh=2ed589a51f9d|url-status=no|access-date=November 21, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121172738/https://www.forbes.com/sites/joewalsh/2020/11/20/who-is-sidney-powell-meet-trumps-new-top-conspiracy-theorist/?sh=2ed589a51f9d|archive-date=2020-11-21}}</ref><ref name=":8">{{Cite news|last=Bump|first=Philip|title=Here's how seriously you should take the Trump legal team's conspiracy theories|language=en-US|work=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]]|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2020/11/19/heres-how-seriously-you-should-take-trump-legal-teams-conspiracy-theories/|url-status=no|access-date=November 20, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120033602/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2020/11/19/heres-how-seriously-you-should-take-trump-legal-teams-conspiracy-theories/|archive-date=2020-11-20|issn=0190-8286}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite news|last=Qiu|first=Linda|date=November 19, 2020|title=How Sidney Powell inaccurately cited Venezuela's elections as evidence of U.S. fraud.|language=en-US|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/19/technology/sidney-powell-venezuela.html|url-status=no|access-date=November 20, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119232027/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/19/technology/sidney-powell-venezuela.html|archive-date=2020-11-19|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>。鮑威爾並指控其他共和黨和民主黨候選人利用Dominion公司行賄，以確保選舉結果對己方有利<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/526798-ernst-trump-lawyer-claim-that-candidates-pay-to-rig-elections-absolutely|title=Ernst: Trump lawyer claim that candidates pay to rig elections 'absolutely outrageous'|first=Lauren|last=Vella|date=November 19, 2020|newspaper=[[The_Hill_(newspaper)|The Hill]]|accessdate=2020-12-16|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120033548/https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/526798-ernst-trump-lawyer-claim-that-candidates-pay-to-rig-elections-absolutely|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年1月8日，[[推特|推特]]永久停用了鮑威爾的帳戶<ref>{{Cite web|title=Twitter permanently suspends Flynn, Sidney Powell, says they engaged in 'harmful activity' related to QAnon|url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/twitter-permanently-suspends-flynn-sidney-powell-says-engaged-in-harmful-activity-related-to-qanon|accessdate=2021-02-02|date=2021-01-08|last=Singman|first=Brooke|work=Fox News|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320124312/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/twitter-permanently-suspends-flynn-sidney-powell-says-engaged-in-harmful-activity-related-to-qanon|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

